strings: <voice_0x010010D2><se_high>Dye: How many times have I told you to go to hell? But you can always come back. T. Monk!
<voice_0x010010D3><se_high>Dye: Everything changes when you meet people who travel all year.
<voice_0x010010D5><se_high>Dye: see your face! I have lost my magic! Traces of glorious youth have disappeared!
